Reaction mechanism and shell effects from the

Thin samples pressed between two Al or Fe foils
Cross-sections were calculated by comparing the no of
counts of the sample with those of the standard used
Aluminium foils used for long lived isotopes,
Fe-56 foils used for short lived isotopes,
The energy-error was due to poor geometry.
